4
00:00:18,949 --> 00:00:20,989
Jadi, kumpulkan mereka.

5
00:00:22,289 --> 00:00:25,190
Tiap bencana didahului oleh tanda peringatan.

6
00:00:31,769 --> 00:00:34,739
Mata-mata dari Utara

7
