784
00:54:04,960 --> 00:54:06,030
Wakil Direktur.

785
00:54:08,329 --> 00:54:10,030
Tutup gerbang utama dan terus terima pasien.

786
00:54:11,630 --> 00:54:13,670
Para tentara bisa saja melihat. Jadi, matikan semua lampu,

787
00:54:13,670 --> 00:54:14,840
kecuali di ruang operasi dan Pusat Medis Darurat.

788
00:54:17,039 --> 00:54:20,739
"Rumah Sakit Gwangju Pyeonghwa"

789
00:54:32,489 --> 00:54:34,219
Makanlah meski kamu tidak lapar.

790
00:54:34,920 --> 00:54:36,730
Kamu belum makan seharian.

791
00:54:40,800 --> 00:54:42,059
Intuisimu

792
00:54:42,869 --> 00:54:44,829
