797
00:54:56,949 --> 00:54:58,550
Dia tampak sama seperti biasanya bagiku.

798
00:55:00,780 --> 00:55:04,019
Benar, bukan? Aku manusia kenari.

799
00:55:09,530 --> 00:55:10,889
Maafkan aku.

